\id LUK Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h LUKA
\toc1 LUKA
\toc2 Luka
\toc3 Luk
\mt1 LUKA
\mt2 (The Gospel According to Luke)
\imt1 Olthangthen Luka Cabu Kawng
\ip Pathen loh a cungkuem a lungnah dongah pilnam boeih kah khangkung la Jesuh halo. Hekah he ol panit he kungpuei la a khueh. Pathen kah lungnah Kawng a dangkah a kawng dongah n'hmuh thai. Samaria Hlang then kawng (10.25-37), Tu hma kawng (15.1-7), Capa aka hma (15.11-32). Jesuh mangmu aka coi im la a caeh kawng (19.1-10) neh hlang thloh laihmu pataeng a duek tomah daemnah (23.39-43) Luka cabu dongah ni dawk a thui.
\ip Luka Olthangthen long tah Pathen Mueihla Cim kawng he a naep la a thui. Baptistma Johan he a manu bung khuiah ah Mueihla neh baetawt coeng (1.15) a ti. Mary taengah khaw , “Mueihla Cim nang taengah ha rhum ni” (1.35) a ti nah. Jesuh Khaw Mueihla hnukah a vai (4.1, 14, 18; 10.21) tih Mueihla he tah a lenkoek kutdoe ni (11.13) tila a cang puei.
\ip Jesuh he thangthuinah olpuei la a khuehnah kawng khaw Luka loh a thui bal. Baptistma a dang vaengah (3.21), hnukbang a tuek vaengah (6.12), hnukbang rhoek a dawt vaengah (9.18), thinglam dongkah a hingnah a pat tom vaengah (23.34, 46) khawt thangthui. Thangthuinah neh tukkai tih thuinuetnah pathum a thui (11.5-9; 18.1-8, 9-14).
\ip Khodaeng lungma ngaithuennah kawng olpuei la a thui. Amih hamla olthangthen a thui pah (4.18; 7.22), amih loh Pathen yoethennah a dang (6.20), amih te buhloeikung la a khue (14.13, 21), khodaeng Lazarus loh vaan a pha (16.20, 22), na khuehtawn te khodaeng rhoek ham tael pah (12.33) a ti.
\ip Jesuh pumtak la thohkoepnah om ti te Luka loh rhep a thui. Jesuh loh nga a caak (24.42, 43). Te dongah Jesuh thohkoepnah he mueihla bueng pawt a pum taksa rhoe thoo a ti. A thokoepnah he oltak la om tih hlanghing a mueimang mailai bal moenih. Luka loh Caeltueih rhoek kah Bibinah cabu he khaw koep a tael bal.
\ip Olthangthen cabu he Jesuh vaan la a lueinah kawng neh a bawt sak.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 I. Olrhannah \ior 1. 1-4\ior*
\io1 II. Hlang Capa kah hlanghing tukkainah \ior 1. 5—2. 52\ior*
\io1 III. Hlang Capa kah baptisma, rhuirhong, noemcainah \ior 3. 1—4. 13\ior*
\io1 IV. Hlang Capa loh tonghma, manghai boei la bibinnah \ior 4. 14—9. 50\ior*
\io1 V. Hlang Capa Galilee lamloh Jerusalem la \ior 9. 51—19. 44\ior*
\io1 VI. Hlang Capa Israel mang kah pumpaeknah \ior 19. 45—23. 56\ior*
\io1 VII. Hlang Capa thohkoepnah neh Vaan la lueinah \ior 24. 1-53\ior*
